      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs directly map to clinical failure modes (fatigue initiation governed by peak stress correlated with stiffness and yield force).",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield force are the primary mechanical determinants of fatigue life under cyclic spinal loading. Force at 40 mm displacement characterizes post-yield behavior relevant to worst-case loading. All three QoIs are directly relevant to the COU."
